title: 'Barbarian'!!!
description:
The no. 1 movie in America is a depraved, completely unpredictable horror movie: hallelujah! Sean and Amanda are joined by Chris Ryan (2:00) to talk about this wonderful freak show before Sean is joined by writer-director Zach Cregger (53:00).

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
Guests: Chris Ryan and Zach Cregger
Producer: Bobby Wagner
